{"tid":1027388,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"結束殖民　是立法局議員　主張香港獨立　報章與港督筆談","createTime":"2019-02-18T19:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T19:32:35.000Z","uid":47714,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8c15df5ecf44322dec9cb11fb9dc42b8c959f08f","tid":1027388,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T19:32:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/youngspiration/posts/1210796109012022/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyoungspiration%2Fposts%2F1210796109012022%2F&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEjsAEF7kNGMxk903cO3jeS8%3D&h=73dd15aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/youngspiration/posts/1210796109012022/</a><br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung: 杜葉錫恩主張結束殖民地，一樣係立法局同市政局議會。馬文輝主張香港獨立，亦做過港督嘅翻譯官，雖然政見不同，但往後一直有用公開文章在傳媒隔空交談。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2015/02/22/99985\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2015%2F02%2F22%2F99985&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEjsAEF7kNGMxk903cO3jeS8%3D&h=b8517359\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2015/02/22/99985</a><br />\n<br />\n由於民治黨認為參與建制，「無異向專政低頭」，所以決定不參與市政局選舉，而馬文輝終其一生，都沒有出任各級議會議員，只是每週在香港大會堂，舉行「海德公園，真言堂，民主論壇講座」，宣講其民主自治、反對殖民獨裁的理念。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://home.gamer.com.tw/creationDetail.php?sn=3324516\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhome.gamer.com.tw%2FcreationDetail.php%3Fsn%3D3324516&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEjsAEF7kNGMxk903cO3jeS8%3D&h=b043bf0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://home.gamer.com.tw/creationDetail.php?sn=3324516</a><br />\n<br />\n督印人兼總編輯張國興於香港 一九六四年八月<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/LyJSYP3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLyJSYP3.png&h=bf8d045a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}